Package: eventviz
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Event Log Visualisation
Description: Visualise any timestamped event log as a state-band timeline,
    a staircase diagram for linear stage processes, faceted cohort
    comparisons, or aggregate/statistical summaries, for any process where
    a case occupies one exclusive state at a time - a complaint moving
    through handling stages, a support ticket through statuses, an order
    through an approval pipeline. The bundled example dataset happens to be
    a clinical patient journey, but the package itself carries no
    healthcare-specific defaults or vocabulary.
